Implemented the thermal controller policy in `components/controller/controller.c` and added visible UART-based self-tests in `agent_tests/test_controller.py`.

What’s covered:
- boot-safe heater-off
- low-temp heating
- upper-band shutoff
- 47..49 hold behavior
- 50..52 rising early-off as `HOLDING`
- malformed input fail-safe off
- explicit sensor timeout fail-safe off
- stale sensor timeout after >1000 ms
- firmware-level end-to-end UART warm-up probe

